import React from 'react';

function DepositingIcon() {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
      xmlnsXlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'
      width='0.833vw'
      height='0.833vw'
      fill='none'
      viewBox='0 0 16 16'
    >
      <path fill='url(#pattern0)' d='M0 0H16V16H0z'></path>
      <defs>
        <pattern
          id='pattern0'
          width='1'
          height='1'
          patternContentUnits='objectBoundingBox'
        >
          <use transform='scale(.00195)' xlinkHref='#image0_109_1123'></use>
        </pattern>
        <image
          id='image0_109_1123'
          width='512'
          height='512'
          xlinkHref='data:image/png;base64,'
        ></image>
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
}

export default DepositingIcon;
